# Terminology (compact)

**Layers:** Vercel (hosting) → Sajtmaskin (app, own-engine default) → v0 (templates/registry/zip; **not** builder codegen streams; optional `V0_FALLBACK_BUILDER` prefers v0 `demoUrl` in preview) → demo sites (user sites; “demo URL” usually means our preview/deploy, not legacy `*.vusercontent.net`).

**Start modes →** `/builder?buildMethod=...`: `wizard` | `category` (v0-templates / Template tab) | `audit` | `freeform` — Swedish UI **Fritext**, code **`freeform`**.

**Three words:** **Scaffold** = runtime starter (`src/lib/gen/scaffolds/`). **Dossier** = external template research (`research/.../dossiers/`). **Artifact** = generated JSON/embeddings consumed by code. **Mall (builder)** = v0-templates gallery — **not** `vercel.com/templates` (**Vercel mall** = research lane → dossiers/artifacts/scaffold ranking). Never call runtime scaffolds plain “templates”.

**Builder model lanes:** model lane (build stream), product lane (prompt assist), polish lane (`SAJTMASKIN_POLISH`), **Resonemang** = flag not a lane. Don’t mix scaffold/Vercel-mall research with lanes.

**Aliases → canonical:** Varicell → Vercel, Veenol → v0.

**semantics / semantic / embedding:** HTML **semantik** ≠ ML **semantisk sökning** / **inbäddning**; code identifiers stay English.

**Legacy docs:** Older plans may mention a removed Cursor multi-agent orchestrator — not part of the product runtime.

**Own-engine pipeline (rough):** prompt assist → orchestration → scaffold → `orchestrate.ts` → `system-prompt.ts` → stream → autofix/merge. **Custom instructions:** `defaults.ts` — CORE always; EXTENDED when scaffold `off`.

**BuildMethod:** `wizard` | `category` | `audit` | `freeform` | `kostnadsfri`. **BuildIntent:** `website` | `app` | `template` (UI **Kompakt**). **`own-engine`** in metadata; **egen motor** in Swedish UI only.

**Theme vs Figma vs v0 DS:** `designTheme` / `themeColors` ≠ Figma attachment ≠ `v0DesignSystemId` — don’t conflate.

**Project / chat / version:** DB project + chats + file snapshots; preview URL; optional legacy v0 IDs.

**Preview:** in-app Next preview; optional v0 `demoUrl` if fallback flag; degraded env placeholders in `config/ai_models/` + `user_degraded_env.txt`; Sandbox = opt-in server test.

**Deploy:** version files → images → Vercel API → URL.

**Picker (reference):** `UnifiedElementPicker`, `UiElementPicker`, `UiElementPickerPreview`.

**IDs (examples):** `appProjectId`, `v0ProjectId`, `demoUrl` (legacy v0), `buildMethod`, `buildIntent`.

**See:** `docs/architecture/repository-and-platform.md`, `docs/architecture/README.md`, `docs/README.md`, `docs/schemas/README.md`, `docs/plans/README.md`.
